I am from Pakistan and i always thought that why did they divide our motherland. probably for their own interest and played a religious card. this song puts my feelings in words. 
one of my elder who saw Pre-partition  time told me once that " angraiz jate jate bhi chaal Chal Gaya aur hamain taqseem Kar Gaya". 
I wish to see re uniting India Pakistan just like reunification of Germany.
